# Aura Calculator

A responsive calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features

- Basic Arithmetic Operations
- Modulus (%)
- Decimal Support
- Backspace
- Clear (AC)
- Keyboard Support
- Division by Zero Handling
- Responsive UI

## Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

